de.hsb.ms.syn.common.net

Class NetMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.hsb.ms.syn.common.net.NetMessage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class NetMessage
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Value object wrapper for messages that are sent over network. Every NetMessage has got a String message and may optionally have extra data (Map format) to be accessed (this implementation is similar to Android's Bundle class). In order to instantiate NetMessage objects, it is advised to use the NetMessageFactory class by invoking its create() method.
    Author:
    Marcel
